HEADWORD: Tarsorrhaphy
<hw>Tar*sor"rha*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Tarsus</ets> + Gr. <grk>"rafh`</grk> seam, fr. <?/ to
